<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an die Juden Michael, Lazarus und Mose</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen Schulden gegenüber Eltern der Adressaten Unkenntnis mit, da man Quittungen über deren Bezahlung besitzt, und verweist auf den Rechtsweg. Auf den Brief wollte ihr Bote nicht warten, weshalb man ihn Kaufleuten zur Zustellung mitgegeben hatte.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_198" id="97v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_198_r1l1">Mıchel / Laʒaro / vnd Moyſen / Juden / des Jacob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l2">Rapen Juden Sünen / . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_198_r1l3">Mıchel / Laʒare / vnd Moyſes / . Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l4">ſchulde <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / die vvir ew von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l5">Alſo / wiſſen vvir cʒü der cʒeit von dheiner ſchulde nicht / . Dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l6">vvir vvaren vor <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlıchen 
<del rend="strikethrough">Juden / die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> el </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſchuldig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l9">
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd </del> darvmb 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough"> iren </del> quitbrief 
<add><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1575921514942_442"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> / . vnd getrawen 
<del rend="strikethrough"> kl </del> ew vvol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l10">daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns </del> von der vordrung laʒʒet / . vver es aber daʒ Jr davon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l11">nicht cʒelaſſen mainet / Dewcht ew dann / daʒ Jr cʒü vns ıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l12">cʒeſprechen het / Darvmb wöllen wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l13">mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gewalt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eins rechten ſein / an den ſteten da </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l14">wir das pıllichen tün ſüllen / . Hett Jr aber cʒü dheinen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l16"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒeſprechen / Darvmb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l17">mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt 
<del rend="strikethrough"> eins </del> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſlewnige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l20">helffen wenn wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / ſo <expan>diſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l22">cʒü den Jr cʒeſprechen het / anheim ſind / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746430269_6340">Vnd das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746432589_6345">wir ew vor 
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del></ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746436099_6355">auch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746434579_6350">alſo </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746438899_6360"><expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> bote </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746440659_6365"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt nicht </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746442093_6370"><expan>wart<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvolt / vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746444429_6375">do <expan>gab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir den brief <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746449403_6385"><expan>kauflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746447112_6380">daʒ ſie ew den <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> / vnd vviſſen nicht </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746451684_6390">ob ew derſelb brief noch <expan>vvorde<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746453978_6395">ſey <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ̃ . </ab><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1576746456463_6400"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>vvalpurg<ex>is</ex></expan> / ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab></add> <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_line_1575921870319_483"><expan>D<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
<note place="bottomcentral"><ab facs="#facs_198_r1l26"> <expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> der 
<add><ab facs="#facs_198_line_1575921897221_493"><expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> </ab></add> brief ward <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd beſigelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l29">aber der bote 
<del rend="strikethrough">lie </del> lieff hinvvegk vnd nam des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l32">niht vnd ſprach doch cʒu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>meiſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l34">Er wolt der Antvvurtt <expan>beẏte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd warten des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r1l36">niht <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt etc </ab></note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_198" id="97v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Michel Lazaro und Moysen, juden, des Jacob Rapen juden sünen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Michel Lazare und Moyses, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                        schulde <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die wir ew von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also wissen wir czü der czeit von dheiner
                        schulde nicht; dann wir waren vor <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlichen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> schuldig, darumb wir quitbrief
                                    <add><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, und getrawen ew wol,
                        daz ir von der vordrung lazzet. Wer es aber, daz ir davon nicht czelassen
                        mainet, dewcht ew dann, daz ir czü uns iht czesprechen het, darumb wöllen
                        wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen
                        gewalt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eins rechten sein an den steten, da wir
                        das pillichen tün süllen. Hett ir aber czü dheinen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czesprechen, darumb
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü den ir czesprechen het, anheim
                        sind; <add>und das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew vor auch
                                <add>also</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>;
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> bote
                                    <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt nicht
                                <expan>wart<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt und do
                                <expan>gab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den brief
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kauflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <add>daz sie ew den
                                        <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, und wissen nicht, ob ew
                            derselb brief noch <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> sey
                                    <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Walpurg<ex>is</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</add>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. <app>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> der
                                        <add><expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan></add> brief ward
                                        <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und besigelt aber der
                                bote lieff hinwegk und nam des niht und sprach doch czu
                                        <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, er wolt der
                                antwurtt <expan>beyte<ex>n</ex></expan> und warten, des niht
                                        <expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist etc. </note>
</app></ab></div>
</div></body>
</text>
